      "content": "Gremlins? I'm not sure what you mean by that. We don't have any issues with pests or anything like that in the warehouse. I was looking for more technical or administrative reasons. \n\nCould you expand on point 3? What kind of equipment malfunctions usually lead to these specific kinds of small, consistent shortages in the digital logs?",
